                    $('.' + titletext + '').wrapAll('&lt;div class="anchorwrap"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;');

                    $(this).parent().nextAll('.anchorwrap:first').slideToggle();

                //update master too
                var rightPageIT = new RegExp('it/content', 'i').test(location.pathname);


                if ($.cookie('cookieAgreeR') != 'yes') {

                    $('body').prepend('&lt;div id="cookiewrap" style="background: #002844; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid #ffffff"&gt;&lt;div id="cookieselector" style="margin: 0 auto; width: 980px; padding: 15px 5px;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;');

                    }

                    $('#cookieselector').append('&lt;div style="clear:both;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;');

                $('.cookielink').click(function () {
                    // set agree cookie &amp; reload page?

                }
